PXDFAUD.original: ~z~When I get the money, man... I will build parks, I will sponsor kids, I will save lives...
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~等我有钱了，兄弟...我就造公园，我就资助孩子，我就挽救生命...

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You can't be fucking with Playboy X. This is my town, my town, motherfucker. Remember that?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你丫惹不起Playboy X。这是我的城市，我的城市，狗逼玩意。记住了？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Yo, what you doin'? You got rid of Dwayne already?
~z~business is tough. I ain't a cold person.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~生意不好做啊。我不是个冷漠的人。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Dwayne, I dealt with Playboy. You should know that he asked me to end you first.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Dwayne，我干掉Playboy了。有件事得告诉你，是他先叫我杀你的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You know, he looks at me like he wants me dead.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~他看我的时候眼睛里就是一股杀意。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~This punk ass bitch gonna get himself killed in here.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~这个狗逼贱人是在自寻死路。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~People respected me, I made a difference.
~z~said you disrespected him, called him mad...
~z~Hey I didn't say that. Man, you cold.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~这我可没说过。兄弟，你太冷酷了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You gone crazy just like Dwayne, son. You gotta be wrong in the head if you think you can step to this shit.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你和Dwayne一样，都疯了，小子。要是觉得这事你能办妥，一开始你就错了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I can't do it myself. He was my boy back in the day.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我自己下不了手。这小子是我一手带大的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Now, I will give you a lot of money.
~z~I thought the old dog woulda put up more of a fight!
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我还以为那老狗会反抗得猛一点！

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Nah, fuck that shit. I ain't ready to go out yet. I need you to get him for me.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~算了，门都没有。我还不打算死。我需要你帮我解决他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, man. We was tight. You fake like the rest of them.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操你妈的，我们明明那么铁。你和他们一样虚伪。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I thought you was my homeboy. That you was gonna put Playboy down for me. What you doing here?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我还以为你是我的同伴，会帮我解决Playboy。你来这干嘛？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I put Dwayne out of his misery.
~z~You in it with Playboy. You and him is trying to take me down.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你跟Playboy联手，你跟他是想杀了我。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Might just let him do it, put a cap in my dome. End it all.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~说不定这样也好，给我做个了结，一了百了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~It was you or Dwayne, I chose Dwayne.
~z~You can't predict what people will become.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~谁都不知道一个人会变成什么样。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You didn't change the game, the game changed you.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你没有改变游戏，游戏改变了你。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You did what you had to do, Niko. You got yourself that money. Good for you.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你做了你该做的事，Niko。那笔钱是你的了。真有你的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Nah, I hear things. Said you and me was too tight now...
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~都传到我耳朵里了。说你和我现在太近了...

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Always hungry though, always wanted more. Maybe I shoulda seen it then. Kept a closer eye on him.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~一直很饥渴，永远不满足。早该想到的，当时就要盯紧他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Holla me sometime, we can hang loose.
~z~You think I got here by letting little bitches like you fuck with me?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~要是你这样的小贱人都能搞我，我会有今天？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You seem like you got my back, Niko. Help me out on this one, dog.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你似乎是帮我的，Niko。帮我一把，老弟。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~ I mean, Dwayne is a killer.
~z~You took down Dwayne, Niko. I see your face, I see the cat that killed my mentor.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你杀了Dwayne，Niko。我看清你的嘴脸了，我知道你老弟杀了我的导师了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Maybe you'll stop by my place sometime though? Hang out with me?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~要么有空你就来看看我？咱俩出去转转？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I tried everything a man could reasonably try and still call his self a man.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~正常人会商量的我都跟他商量了，很给他面子了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I can't do it myself. He was my boy back in the day.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我自己下不了手。这小子是我一手带大的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~On the down low, I think Playboy wants me dead.
~z~It ain't that simple, Dwayne. This is nothing personal.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~事情没那么简单，Dwayne。这不是件小事。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Was going to pay me a lot of money to do it.
~z~All this? It means nothing if you ain't got the heart, Niko
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~还是这些？要是没这个良心，这些都是空的，Niko。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Nah. It'll make me remember the kid too much.
~z~and I changed stuff, and you know me, I do this stuff so I got a chance to do some good in this town.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~于是我转行了，你也懂我，做这行还能给这个城市做点好事。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Well neither do I, man. But if he goes insane, we all dead anyway.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我也不想啊，兄弟。但是一旦他疯起来，我们都得完蛋。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I know what loyalty means, unlike some people. You and me is tight now.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我知道忠诚的意义，不像某些人。咱俩现在是铁哥们了。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Dwayne was like a father to me. I can't be round you no more. It's over between us.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Dwayne就像是我的父亲。我不会再找你了，我们结束了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~That's something I won't be able to forget.
~z~Now, I got into this dope game because it was the only thing that was open to me, man.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我之所以做毒品生意，是因为它是我唯一的出路，兄弟。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, man. We was tight. You fake like the rest of them.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操你妈的，我们明明那么铁。你和他们一样虚伪。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Dwayne, I killed Playboy. You should know that he asked me to end you first.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Dwayne，Playboy我已经杀了。有件事得告诉你，是他先叫我杀你来的。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I'll stick by you 'til the end. Take him out for me.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我会一直支持你的，替我做了他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I'll give you a call sometime soon, Dwayne. Later on.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~那我有空就给你打电话，Dwayne。再见。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Might just let him do it, put a cap in my dome. End it all.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~说不定这样也好，给我做个了结，一了百了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~They made sense inside. Three meals a day, time in the yard, lockdown at eight.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~在里头的时候对头。一日三餐，院子放风，八点回房。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Nah, fuck that shit. I ain't ready to go out yet. I need you to get him for me.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~算了，门都没有。我还不打算死。我需要你帮我解决他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I don't want no beef, but now you and me got some.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我不喜欢怨恨，不过现在我俩有了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Dwayne, it's Niko. You been trying to call me. Say what you gotta say.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Dwayne，我是Niko。你打了这么多个电话，有话直说吧。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I seen where you're living, you should take it.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~嘿，老哥，我见识过你住的地方，房子你留着吧。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Man, you ain't cool. You try to find something to live for, man. Peace.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~兄弟你不行。你得想想自己为什么而活，兄弟。别了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Damn, you done fucked me over in the end.
~z~Always hungry though, always wanted more. Maybe I shoulda seen it then. Kept a closer eye on him.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~一直很饥渴，永远不满足。我早该发现的，盯得他紧一点。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You in it with Playboy. You and him is trying to take me down.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你跟Playboy联手，你跟他是想杀了我。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Fuck you, man. You a fucking snake like the rest of them.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操你妈，狗人。你丫他妈跟他们一样狠毒。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I took shit to the next level, cats like you just can't accept that.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我已经升到了新的境界，你这样的小鬼还无法接受而已。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Shit, man. He was a good kid back in the day.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操，老弟。以前他还是个好孩子。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~But I gotta have the money man. 'Cause all this?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~前提是我得有钱啊，兄弟。你以为是为了这些？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~That's something I won't be able to forget.
~z~Shit, man. He was a good kid back in the day.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操，老弟。以前他还是个好孩子。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I took care of business. I gave him money,
~z~history is a long time. And you only got one chance...
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~历史的时间很长。而你只有一次机会...

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Shit - you nothing but a cold hearted killer, man.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操－你除了是个冷血杀手就什么都不是了，兄弟。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~He did some crazy shit, too. I mean, everyone does.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~他也做过垃圾事。所有人都会犯错。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~He was going to pay me a lot of money to do it.
~z~Since I got out things just don't make no sense.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~自从我出来后，就没有对头的事了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Not such a big man now, are you?
~z~I don't have many friends left, you know.
~z~but because I won't bow down to him and treat him like he The Almighty,
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~就因为我不对他卑躬屈膝，不把他当上帝供着，

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You right. I can't give you no money for helping me, dog. But I'll stick by your ass.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~确实，你帮我我也给不了你几个子儿，小子。不过我会始终站在你这边。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Playboy was your best friend, and he's always been straight with me, more or less.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Playboy曾是你最好的朋友，基本上他对我也是坦诚相待。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~He killed people. He killed that John the Baptist cat. He did what he had to.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~他也杀过人。他杀了那个施洗约翰。他只是做了该做的事。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Something's wrong. Don't nobody come to see me up in here.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~有点不对，没人会来这里见我。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Another motherfucker gone and let the money go to his head.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~又是个迷失自我掉钱眼里的狗逼玩意。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Motherfucker, you think you can touch this shit?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~狗逼玩意，你以为你丫能伤着我？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I don't think you're correct about that.
~z~Fuck you, man. You a fucking snake like the rest of them.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~操你妈，狗人。你丫他妈跟他们一样狠毒。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Now I paid my dues. Now I learned in a hard school, man...
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~现在我得到回报了。现在我在社会上学到了，兄弟...

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~So it's best if we just stay the hell away from each other, man.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~所以我们最好还是不相往来，兄弟。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You seem like you got my back, Niko. Help me out on this one, dog.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你似乎是帮我的，Niko。帮我一把，老弟。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You can't predict what people will become.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~谁都不知道一个人会变成什么样。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I was an example to all the kids, man. You can't take that away from me.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我是孩子们的榜样，兄弟。这你不能否认吧。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Because see me, now I ain't scared of no one, but a motherfuckers says he's gonna kill me?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~因为你看我，我谁都不怕，结果有个狗逼说要杀我？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Since I got out things just don't make no sense.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~自从我出来后，就没有对头的事了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I showed you the world, gangster. You don't control this shit.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我带你见了世面，小子。你把持不住的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Playboy was your best friend, and he's always been straight with me, more or less.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~Playboy曾是你最好的朋友，基本上他对我也是坦诚相待。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I'll stick by you 'til the end. Take him out for me.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我会一直支持你的，替我做了他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~But I got the deed to Playboy's fancy silk sheet loft. You can have it.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~不过Playboy锦衣玉食的顶楼公寓的房产证还在我手里，房子就归你了。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I mean, I am cold, but... motherfucker.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我是说，我确实冷酷，不过...狗日的。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I thought you was my homeboy. That you was gonna put Playboy down for me. What you doing here?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我还以为你是我的同伴，会帮我解决Playboy。你来这干嘛？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I mean, where the love? Where's your heart, homie?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我是说，你的爱呢？你的良心呢，老哥？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~he's gone crazy. I mean he's gone. Prison does that.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~他已经疯了。我是说他回不来了。监狱让他成了这样。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You right. I can't give you no money for helping me, son.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~确实。你帮我我也给不了你几个子儿，小子。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~He was in prison a long time - maybe you guys should talk...
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~他号子蹲太久了，要么你俩沟通沟通...

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Ain't got much else to do. So long, Niko.
~z~What the fuck you playin' at, motherfucker?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你丫他妈搞什么呢，狗比玩意儿？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Maybe your problem is that you don't understand that. I'll be seeing you soon.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你的问题大概就出在不明白这一点，走着瞧吧。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Even if you kill me, you gonna have this whole town after your ass.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~就算你杀了我，城里还有无数人会来追杀你。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You cold, man, you cold. Taking a cat down in his prime. I was an innovator.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~冷酷的男人，冷酷。正当年的时候把人给杀了。我是革新者。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~You shouldn't have asked me to kill Dwayne, Playboy.
~z~On the down low, I think Playboy wants me dead.
~z~Make this easy on yourself, Dwayne. It's business, it ain't nothing personal.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~看开点，Dwayne。这是公事，不是什么私仇。(BETA)

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Now Dwayne after both our asses now, for sure. Come back to the penthouse.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~现在我俩都得被Dwayne追杀了，真的。回我公寓来。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Argh. I was someone, you know. I made it. I changed the game.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~啊，怎么说我也是个人物。我做到了，我改变了游戏。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~No, I tried talking. I... I... I tried giving him half of the business.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~早沟通过了。我...我...我跟他说分一半产业给他。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I thought you was money, you a low rate bitch.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我还以为要找的就是你老弟，你个垃圾烂货。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Well, I hope you see some sense.
~z~Do you think that I do? But it's kill or be killed out there. And you got a lunatic after you?
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~你当我喜欢？现在不是干他就是被干。还是说你想被个疯子追杀？

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~I don't know that that is true, Playboy. This town don't belong to nobody.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~我还真不知道这是实话，Playboy。这座城市不属于任何人。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Well what you doin' back here then? Step to it, motherfucker.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~那你丫回来干啥？还不快去，狗逼玩意。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~Man, Dwayne... it's like he thinks it's 1992 and the best you can hope for is a gold chain and a pager.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，Dwayne...他还活在1992年，最大的梦想就是根大金链子和BP机。

PXDFAUD.original: ~z~They made sense inside. Three meals a day, time in the yard, lockdown at eight.
PXDFAUD.translated: ~z~在里头的时候对头。一日三餐，院子放风，八点回房。
